<div class="job-details">


<ul>
	<li><strong>Area:&nbsp;</strong>Fourways</li>
	<li><strong>Working hours:</strong>&nbsp;Monday to Friday 10:00 &ndash; 14:00</li>
	<li><strong>Duties:&nbsp;</strong>Basic admin duties, answering calls, following up with clients, greeting clients and maintaining a rapport, building relationship with owners, find out their LPG requirements, COC needs, Kitchen LPG services etc. The candidate will need to go see clients at restaurants, hotels, air bnb&rsquo;s, LPG buyers, petrol stations, hardware stores etc). Full training will be provided</li>
