</li>


</ul>

<div class="job-details">


<ul>
	<li><strong>Area:&nbsp;</strong>Atholl</li>
	<li><strong>Children&rsquo;s Ages:&nbsp;</strong>Boys &ndash; 9 (Grade 3) and 12 years (Grade 6)</li>
	<li><strong>Working hours:&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp;Tuesday &ndash; Thursday 13:30 &ndash; 17:30<strong>&nbsp;</strong>&ndash; Ad Hoc Monday&#39;s and Friday&#39;s may be needed but this will be arranged in advance and paid additionally (if the candidate is available)</li>
	<li><strong>School holiday hours:&nbsp;</strong>Monday &ndash; Friday 13:30 &ndash; 17:30 (Monday and Friday afternoons as well as ad hoc mornings may be needed but this will be paid additionally and if the candidate is available)</li>
	<li><strong>Duties:&nbsp;</strong>Collect from school, take to extra murals, run school errands and help with homework/studying (main focus on the Grade 6). During school holidays, plan excursions and keep them busy.</li>
	<li><strong>Special Requirements:&nbsp;</strong>Male/Female, 20-30, sporty to play sports with them at home, tutor experience<strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li>
	<li><strong>Start Date and contract term:&nbsp;</strong>Mid-July/August 2026 &ndash; permanent</li>
